<center><b>
<h1>Bob Jones University</h1><br>
<img src="/graphics/bjcrest.gif"><br>
<hr><center><h2>Accounting Major</h2></center><p>
<a href="#desc">Description of the Major</a><br>
<a href="#course">Course Highlights</a><br>
<a href="#typical">Typical Course Sequence</a><br>
<a href="#facil">Facilities</a><br>
<a href="#faculty">Faculty</a><br>
