<hr><font SIZE=+3>What is this?</font> 
 <hr><img src="pic/top.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>top of the page</i>. <br>
 <br><img src="pic/hom.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>index page for the Linked Word Project</i>.

<br>
 <br><img src="pic/com.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>index of available commentaries</i>. <br>
 <br><img src="pic/hlp.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>helps</i> section. <br>
 <br><img src="pic/nxt.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>next</i> page in a series. <br>
 <br><img src="pic/pre.jpg" border=0  height=24 width =25 >&nbsp;&nbsp;Pushing this button
takes you to the <i>previous</i> page in a series. 
 <br><font SIZE=+4>*</font> The asterisk you see following verbs takes you
 to the parsing for that particular word. <br> <hr> <center>
