<html>
<title>Matthew Chapter 1</title>
<body background="../pic/gray.jpg" text="000000" link="000000" vlink="000000" alink="000000" >
<center><a name=chapter1></a><font size=6>Matthew 1</font></center><hr>
<br>
<a href="mt.html"><img border=0 src="../pic/pre.jpg"></a>
<br>

<br><a name=1>1.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="../g/950.html#976">The book</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1078">of the generation</a> <a href="../g/2400.html#2424">of Jesus</a> <a href="../g/5500.html#5547"> Christ</a>, <a href="../g/5200.html#5207">the son</a> <a href="../g/1100.html#1138">of David</a>, <a href="../g/5200.html#5207">the son</a> <a href="../g/0.html#11">of Abraham</a>.<br>

<br><a name=2>2.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="../g/0.html#11">Abraham</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1080">begat</a> <a href="../g/5650.html#5656"><font size=-1>*</font></a>  <a href="../g/2450.html#2464">Isaac</a>; <a href="../g/1150.html#1161">and</a> <a href="../g/2450.html#2464"> Isaac</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1080">begat</a> <a href="../g/5650.html#5656"><font size=-1>*</font></a>  <a href="../g/2350.html#2384">Jacob</a>; <a href="../g/1150.html#1161">and</a> <a href="../g/2350.html#2384">Jacob</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1080">begat</a> <a href="../g/5650.html#5656"><font size=-1>*</font></a>  <a href="../g/2450.html#2455">Judas</a> <a href="../g/2500.html#2532">and</a> <a href="../g/800.html#846">his</a> <a href="../g/50.html#80"> brethren</a>;<br>

