<br><a name=12>12.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="../g/1150.html#1161">And</a> <a href="../g/3300.html#3326">after</a> <a href="../g/3350.html#3350">they were brought</a> <a href="../g/850.html#897">to Babylon</a>, <a href="../g/2400.html#2423">Jechonias</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1080">begat</a> <a href="../g/5650.html#5656"><font size=-1>*</font></a>  <a href="../g/4500.html#4528">Salathiel</a>; <a href="../g/1150.html#1161">and</a> <a href="../g/4500.html#4528">Salathiel</a> <a href="../g/1050.html#1080">begat</a> <a href="../g/5650.html#5656"><font size=-1>*</font></a>  <a href="../g/2200.html#2216">Zorobabel</a>;<br>

